{"info":{"_postman_id":"681b3bc5-f49b-4fad-ade5-f3b5ed4d9d23","name":"Beach-Flow","description":"<html><head></head><body><p><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?w=1200\" alt=\"Beach\"></p>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>https://beachflow-app-final-production.up.railway.app</code> </p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"beach-flow-api-collection\">Beach-Flow API Collection</h2>\n<p>A comprehensive REST API collection for the <strong>Beach-Flow</strong> platform — a beach discovery, booking, and management application. This collection covers authentication, admin operations, user-facing features, and super-admin capabilities.</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"modules\">Modules</h3>\n<h4 id=\"1-auth-api-7-endpoints\">1. Auth-Api (7 endpoints)</h4>\n<p>Complete authentication lifecycle:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Register</strong> — Create a new user account</li>\n<li><strong>Login</strong> — Authenticate and receive a token</li>\n<li><strong>VerifyOTP</strong> — Verify the one-time password sent during registration</li>\n<li><strong>Resend OTP</strong> — Request a new OTP code</li>\n<li><strong>Forgot-Password</strong> — Initiate the password-reset flow</li>\n<li><strong>Verify-Reset-Code</strong> — Confirm the password-reset code</li>\n<li><strong>Reset Password</strong> — Set a new password</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"2-admin-api-4-endpoints\">2. Admin-Api (4 endpoints)</h4>\n<p>Beach management for administrators:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Get My Beaches</strong> — List beaches owned by the admin</li>\n<li><strong>Add New Beach</strong> — Create a new beach listing</li>\n<li><strong>Update Beach</strong> — Edit an existing beach</li>\n<li><strong>Delete Beach</strong> — Remove a beach listing</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"3-user-api-14-endpoints\">3. User-Api (14 endpoints)</h4>\n<p>User-facing features including beaches, bookings, favorites, reviews, payments, notifications, profiles, and support.</p>\n<h4 id=\"4-supadmin-api\">4. SupAdmin-Api</h4>\n<p>Reserved module for super-admin operations (currently empty).</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"key-workflows\">Key Workflows</h3>\n<div class=\"click-to-expand-wrapper is-table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Flow</th>\n<th>Steps</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Registration</strong></td>\n<td>Register → VerifyOTP (→ Resend OTP if needed)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Password Recovery</strong></td>\n<td>Forgot-Password → Verify-Reset-Code → Reset Password</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Beach Booking</strong></td>\n<td>Browse beaches → Book → Pay → Receive notification</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>User Engagement</strong></td>\n<td>Favorite beaches → Leave reviews → Contact support</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div><hr>\n<h3 id=\"technical-notes\">Technical Notes</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>RESTful design with JSON payloads</li>\n<li>Token-based authentication (include token in <code>Authorization</code> header)</li>\n<li>Role-based access control: <strong>User</strong>, <strong>Admin</strong>, <strong>SuperAdmin</strong></li>\n<li>All endpoints use the <code>{{Base-Url}}</code> collection variable</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>","schema":"https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.0.0/collection.json","toc":[],"owner":"46910696","collectionId":"681b3bc5-f49b-4fad-ade5-f3b5ed4d9d23","publishedId":"2sBXqCNNkB","public":true,"customColor":{"top-bar":"FFFFFF","right-sidebar":"303030","highlight":"FF6C37"},"publishDate":"2026-04-13T19:38:13.000Z"},"item":[{"name":"SupAdmin-Api","item":[],"id":"bfceaef5-022c-4cbb-955f-4881c0a0cee1","_postman_id":"bfceaef5-022c-4cbb-955f-4881c0a0cee1","description":""},{"name":"Admin-Api","item":[{"name":"Get My Beache","id":"46222e02-c9bb-4de0-ba32-00a448853737","protocolProfileBehavior":{"disableBodyPruning":true},"request":{"auth":{"type":"bearer","bearer":{"basicConfig":[{"key":"token","value":"<token>"}]},"isInherited":false},"method":"GET","header":[],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"","options":{"raw":{"language":"js