olProfileBehavior":{"disableBodyPruning":true},"request":{"auth":{"type":"bearer","bearer":{"basicConfig":[{"key":"token","value":"<token>"}]},"isInherited":false},"method":"POST","header":[],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\r\n  \"idCardUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dbtztjban/image/upload/v1776221623/kbxttzpmk7diz9lnmf17.jpg\"\r\n}","options":{"raw":{"language":"json"}}},"url":"{{Base-Url}}/api/users/request-admin","urlObject":{"path":["api","users","request-admin"],"host":["{{Base-Url}}"],"query":[],"variable":[]}},"response":[],"_postman_id":"3e15f540-2157-4cff-a792-c17a404c4277"}],"id":"8876d605-eedf-4dfd-aa3c-196a16739581","description":"<p>This folder contains all user-facing API endpoints for the Beach e-commerce application. It covers the core functionality available to authenticated users, organized across the following areas:</p>\n<p><strong>Beaches</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Browse all beaches, search by name, view individual beach details, and discover top-rated beaches.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bookings</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create new bookings and retrieve the current user's booking history.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Favorites</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Toggle beaches as favorites and view the user's saved favorites list.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>User Profile</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>View and edit the authenticated user's profile information.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Notifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Retrieve the user's notifications.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Reviews</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Submit reviews for beaches.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Payments</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Initiate a payment and generate a payment link.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Support</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create a support ticket.</li>\n</ul>\n","_postman_id":"8876d605-eedf-4dfd-aa3c-196a16739581"},{"name":"test","id":"866ade1d-eb75-469c-b66f-94d83c083ea3","protocolProfileBehavior":{"disableBodyPruning":true},"request":{"auth":{"type":"bearer","bearer":{"basicConfig":[{"key":"token","va